8.la: Seuli in Corea, passio sanctorum [1|Sebastiani Nam I-gwan] et novem sociorum*, martyrum, ...; commemorantur item sanctae martyres [2|Lucia Kim], [3|Catharina Yi], vidua, atque ipsius filia [4|Magdalena Cho], virgo, ... occubuerunt.[/][/]*Quorum nomina: sancti [5|Ignatius Kim Che-jun], [6|Carolus Cho Shin-ch'ol], [7|Columba Kim Hyo-im], virgo; [8|Magdalena Pak Pong-son] et [9|Perpetua Hong Kum-ju], viduae; [10|Iulitta Kim], [11|Agatha Chon Kyong-hyob], [12|Magdalena Ho Kye-im].
